title: GMFB: Lots of Gold Jackets
itunes:title: GMFB: Lots of Gold Jackets
description:
On the #GMFB podcast: The group shares their interesting travel issues getting to Hall of Fame Weekend (1:29); Peter’s calm in the face of travel issues (4:13); The group discuss their favorite part of experiencing the Hall of Fame (5:39) and doing a show from the Hall of Fame Parade (14:48); Kyle discusses his prep for another hosting gig (18:49) and finally, we hear a piece from HOF inductee Kurt Warner from the show (23:35)

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
